      • getLatestNBuildsName

        public List<String> getLatestNBuildsName(String configurationName,
                                int num)
        returns the name of the latest build accordingly with build names. In this method we assume that build names are in the form BUILD_<sequence_number>. The build with higher sequence number is selected. The algorithm used in this method is inappropriate, though very fast; the best way of selecting latest build would be to get all build's endDate and select the one with the most recent date. if num is -1 all builds will be returned
        Parameters:
        configuration -
        Returns:
